This Privacy Policy explains how WandernGuide collects, uses, and shares information about users of our mobile application.

Information we collect
When you use WandernGuide, we may collect information about you, including:

Personal information: We may collect personal information such as your name and email address if you choose to provide it to us.

Device information: We may collect information about the device you are using to access WandernGuide, including the type of device, operating system, and device settings.

Usage information: We may collect information about how you use WandernGuide, including the features you use and the content you view.

Location information: We may collect information about your location if you give us permission to do so. We use this information to provide you with location-based features, such as recommendations for nearby hiking trails.

How we use your information
We use the information we collect to:

Provide and improve WandernGuide: We use your information to provide and improve our mobile application, including developing new features and analyzing usage data.

Personalize your experience: We use your information to personalize your experience with WandernGuide, including providing recommendations for hiking trails and other outdoor activities.

Communicate with you: We may use your information to communicate with you about WandernGuide, including sending you updates and notifications.

How we share your information
We may share your information with third parties in the following circumstances:

Service providers: We may share your information with service providers that help us provide and improve WandernGuide, such as hosting providers and analytics providers.

Legal requirements: We may share your information if we believe it is necessary to comply with a legal obligation or protect our rights or the rights of others.

Business transactions: We may share your information in connection with a business transaction, such as a merger or acquisition.

Your choices
You can choose not to provide personal information to WandernGuide, but this may limit your ability to use certain features of the application. You can also control how we use location information by adjusting your device settings.

Security
We take reasonable measures to protect the information we collect from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction.

Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we make material changes, we will notify you by email or by posting a notice in WandernGuide.

Contact us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at support@wandernguide.com.
